lead_paragraph: To a man, and starting with the head coach, the Nebraska Cornhuskers said their first loss of the season motivates them more than disappoints them and that there would be no emotional hangover when they play No. 6 Ohio State in the second of two straight difficult road games.

headline.print_headline: Riley: No. 9 Huskers to Show Up 'Mad' Against No. 6 Ohio St.
headline.main: Riley: No. 9 Huskers to Show Up 'Mad' Against No. 6 Ohio St.
